      <p class="lead hero-subtitle">A complete, honest guide to becoming a mortgage broker &mdash; how to register with the NMLS, finish the 20-hour SAFE course, pass the SAFE MLO exam, and turn your license into a real business. Written by a 7&times; Scotsman Guide Top Producer with $500M+ closed, not a course-selling middleman.</p>
