          <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Yes, many people start part-time, especially while transitioning from another career. The licensing can be completed around a full-time job, and once you're licensed and sponsored, you can scale your hours as your pipeline grows. If you already hold a real estate, insurance, or financial-services license, the role layers naturally onto your existing relationships.</div></div>
